welcome_message_body: Welcome to Winona, a charming city nestled in the picturesque bluffs of Southern Minnesota. Get ready to explore our vibrant arts scene, scenic hiking trails, and delicious local cuisine. We can't wait for you to experience all that our city has to offer!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal handles all freight and cargo operations at Municipal Airport.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
